---
import Panel from './Panel.astro';
---

<Panel title="MTX OWNERSHIP & CASINO ECONOMICS" class="ownership-panel">
  <div class="ownership-intro">
    <p class="highlight-text">
      <strong>Owning MTX makes you an owner of the casino.</strong>
    </p>
    <p class="intro-text">
      The MTX Casino operates on a community-owned model where MTX token holders collectively own the casino's reserves, liquidity, and future profits. There's no private entity extracting value‚Äîthe casino belongs to the MTX ecosystem.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ownership-benefits">
    <h3>üé∞ How MTX Ownership Works</h3>
    <ul class="benefits-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Direct Casino Ownership:</strong> MTX holders collectively own the CasinoReserve smart contract, which holds all casino funds. There's no corporation or private entity‚Äîthe reserve IS the casino, and MTX holders ARE the owners.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Governance Rights:</strong> MTX gives you weighted voting power to adjust casino parameters (game odds, fee percentages, reserve allocations), enable new games, and pause systems in emergencies.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Value Accrual:</strong> As players lose bets, a portion flows to the CasinoReserve (backing MTX value), liquidity pools (supporting MTX trading), and is burned (reducing supply). Winners withdraw from the same reserve.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Sustainable Model:</strong> Unlike traditional casinos with profit extraction, the MTX Casino reinvests all revenue into liquidity, reserves, and burns‚Äîdirectly benefiting MTX holders through increased backing and scarcity.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="reserve-liquidity">
    <h3>üíé Casino Reserve & Liquidity</h3>
    
    <div class="section-block">
      <h4>CasinoReserve Contract</h4>
      <p><code>0xCf7Ed3AccA5a467e9e704C703E8D87F634fB0Fc9</code></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> Holds MTX to pay winners and absorb losses</li>
        <li><strong>Funding:</strong> 3% of all bets go to reserve to maintain solvency</li>
        <li><strong>Risk Control:</strong> Max bet limited to reserve size to prevent insolvency</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> All deposits/withdrawals on-chain and auditable</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section-block">
      <h4>Liquidity Pool Allocation</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Allocation:</strong> 10% of all casino revenue flows to liquidity pools</li>
        <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> Ensures MTX has deep liquidity for trading</li>
        <li><strong>Benefit:</strong> Reduces slippage, enables easy entry/exit for holders</li>
        <li><strong>Long-term:</strong> Growing liquidity stabilizes MTX price and supports ecosystem health</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section-block">
      <h4>Revenue Distribution Breakdown</h4>
      <div class="revenue-table">
        <div class="revenue-row">
          <span class="revenue-label">Players (Payouts):</span>
          <span class="revenue-value">85%</span>
          <span class="revenue-desc">Direct winnings paid to lucky players</span>
        </div>
        <div class="revenue-row">
          <span class="revenue-label">Liquidity Pool:</span>
          <span class="revenue-value">10%</span>
          <span class="revenue-desc">Strengthens MTX trading depth</span>
        </div>
        <div class="revenue-row">
          <span class="revenue-label">Casino Reserve:</span>
          <span class="revenue-value">3%</span>
          <span class="revenue-desc">Builds reserve for future payouts</span>
        </div>
        <div class="revenue-row">
          <span class="revenue-label">Development:</span>
          <span class="revenue-value">2%</span>
          <span class="revenue-desc">Funds ongoing development and maintenance</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="revenue-note">
        <em>100% of revenue is accounted for. Zero profit extraction. All value flows back to the ecosystem.</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ownership-vs-traditional">
    <h3>üèõÔ∏è MTX Ownership vs. Traditional Casinos</h3>
    <div class="comparison-grid">
      <div class="comparison-card traditional">
        <h4>üè¢ Traditional Casino</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>‚ùå Private shareholders extract profits</li>
          <li>‚ùå Players have no ownership or governance</li>
          <li>‚ùå House edge benefits corporation, not users</li>
          <li>‚ùå Opaque financials and reserve management</li>
          <li>‚ùå No way for players to participate in upside</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="comparison-card mtx">
        <h4>‚ö° MTX Casino</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>‚úÖ MTX holders collectively own the casino</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Governance rights for all MTX holders</li>
          <li>‚úÖ House edge benefits MTX holders via reserves, liquidity, burns</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Fully transparent on-chain financials</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Holding MTX = owning part of the casino's future value</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ownership-mechanics">
    <h3>‚öôÔ∏è Ownership Mechanics in Action</h3>
    <div class="mechanics-flow">
      <div class="flow-step">
        <strong>1. Player Places Bet</strong>
        <p>Player spends MTX to play slots, blackjack, or roulette</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <strong>2. Bet Processed</strong>
        <p>85% ‚Üí Player payout pool | 10% ‚Üí Liquidity | 3% ‚Üí Reserve | 2% ‚Üí Dev</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <strong>3. Value Accrual</strong>
        <p>Reserve grows, liquidity deepens, dev funds maintenance‚Äîall benefiting MTX holders</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <strong>4. Outcome</strong>
        <p>Win: MTX paid from reserve | Lose: MTX stays in reserve, backing all holders</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ownership-summary">
    <h3>üìä Summary: What MTX Ownership Means</h3>
    <div class="summary-box">
      <p>
        <strong>Owning MTX is like owning shares in a decentralized casino.</strong> 
        Every bet strengthens the reserve, deepens liquidity, and burns supply‚Äîall of which increase the backing and scarcity of your MTX. 
        You have governance rights to shape the casino's future. There's no CEO, no shareholders extracting dividends‚Äîjust a transparent, 
        community-owned protocol where all value flows back to MTX holders.
      </p>
      <p class="summary-note">
        <em>Note: MTX is a utility token, not a security. It provides governance rights and ecosystem access, 
        but does not guarantee profits or represent equity ownership in a legal entity. Always review the 
        <a href="/docs/MTX_Disclaimer.md" target="_blank">Disclaimer</a> before participating.</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ownership-cta">
    <a href="/docs/MTX_Whitepaper.md" target="_blank" class="cta-button">Read Full Whitepaper</a>
    <a href="/docs/MTX_DAO_Governance.md" target="_blank" class="cta-button">Learn About Governance</a>
    <a href="/games/casino/" class="cta-button primary">Play Casino Games</a>
  </div>
</Panel>

<style>
  .ownership-panel {
    margin: 30px auto;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  .ownership-intro {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .highlight-text {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--theme-glow);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    display: block;
  }

  .intro-text {
    color: var(--theme-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .ownership-benefits h3,
  .reserve-liquidity h3,
  .ownership-vs-traditional h3,
  .ownership-mechanics h3,
  .ownership-summary h3 {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--theme-glow);
  }

  .benefits-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .benefits-list li {
    background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.05);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-primary);
    padding: 12px 15px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--theme-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .benefits-list li strong {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
  }

  .section-block {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border: 1px solid var(--theme-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .section-block h4 {
    color: var(--theme-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  .section-block code {
    background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .section-block ul {
    margin: 10px 0 0 20px;
    color: var(--theme-text);
  }

  .section-block ul li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .revenue-table {
    margin: 15px 0;
  }

  .revenue-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 150px 60px 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px;
    background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.03);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .revenue-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .revenue-label {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .revenue-value {
    color: var(--theme-secondary);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .revenue-desc {
    color: var(--theme-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .revenue-note {
    margin-top: 15px;
    color: var(--theme-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .comparison-card {
    border: 2px solid var(--theme-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .comparison-card.traditional {
    border-color: #ff4444;
  }

  .comparison-card.mtx {
    border-color: var(--theme-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--theme-glow);
  }

  .comparison-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .comparison-card.traditional h4 {
    color: #ff6666;
  }

  .comparison-card.mtx h4 {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
  }

  .comparison-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .comparison-card ul li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: var(--theme-text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .mechanics-flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin: 20px 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .flow-step {
    background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.08);
    border: 2px solid var(--theme-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 180px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .flow-step strong {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .flow-step p {
    color: var(--theme-text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .flow-arrow {
    color: var(--theme-secondary);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 10px;
  }

  .summary-box {
    background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.05);
    border: 2px solid var(--theme-primary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--theme-glow);
  }

  .summary-box p {
    color: var(--theme-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .summary-box strong {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
  }

  .summary-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem !important;
    color: var(--theme-secondary) !important;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .summary-note a {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .ownership-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-top: 30px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: var(--theme-bg-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--theme-border);
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--theme-glow);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta-button.primary {
    background: var(--theme-primary);
    color: #000;
  }

  .cta-button.primary:hover {
    background: var(--theme-secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--theme-glow);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .comparison-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .mechanics-flow {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .flow-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .revenue-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 5px;
    }

    .revenue-label,
    .revenue-value,
    .revenue-desc {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
